<BaseLayout title="About — Christopher Martino" current="about"><section class="text-page"><p class="eyebrow">About</p><h1>Christopher Martino is a New York–based artist working primarily in painting and drawing.</h1><div class="prose"><p>His work moves between observation, construction, and memory, using quiet interiors, figures, and architectural spaces as sites of psychological tension.</p><p>He holds a BFA from Pratt Institute and an MFA from the School of Visual Arts.</p></div></section></BaseLayout>
